===Etymology===
From {{der|en|hi|रुपीया|tr=rupīyā|sc=Deva}}, variant of {{m|hi|रुपया|tr=rupayā|sc=Deva}} or {{der|en|ur|رپيا|tr=rupayā|sc=ur-Arab}}, coined by [[w:Mughal Empire|Mughal emperor]] [[w:Sher Shah Suri|Sher Shah Suri]] (1540–1545) from {{der|en|sa|रूप्यक||[[silver]] [[coin]]}}, from {{m|sa|रूप्य||[[wrought]] silver}}.

