* {{hyphenation|ru|pee|lang=en}}

===Noun===
{{en-noun}}

# The common name for the [[monetary]] [[currency|currencies]] used in modern [[India]], [[Mauritius]], [[Nepal]], [[Pakistan]], the [[Seychelles]], or [[Sri Lanka]], often abbreviated [[₨]].
# A [[silver]] [[coin]] [[circulate|circulating]] in [[India]] between the 16th and 20th centuries, [[weigh|weighing]] one [[tola]] (formerly 170–180&nbsp;[[troy grain]]s; from 1833, 180&nbsp;troy grains).

